{"tid":277239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"決戰ISIS「國都」：拉卡圍城戰，敘利亞正式開打","createTime":"2017-06-09T12:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T13:01:32.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"592c6f8b67c92b0c7b202c40aecebab803d9aeba","tid":277239,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/2509016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8662%2F2509016&d=lcEK0%2F7e%2FofNWhS4pCQShaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7878eb38\" target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/2509016</a><br />\n<br />\n對抗ISIS的聯軍戰役，即將進入對決時刻。活動在敘利亞北境、以庫德族戰士為骨幹的「敘利亞民主力量」（SDF），周二宣布正式對「ISIS國都」、敘利亞東部大城拉卡（Raqqa）發動圍城︿<br />\n<br />\n位於敘利亞北部的拉卡，自2014年1月被ISIS攻陷以來，就一直被當作「國都」使用，並與伊拉克的摩蘇爾，並列為ISIS的兩大中樞城市。然而隨著聯軍的進擊，近兩年來ISIS在敘利亞、伊拉克的「國土」也一一被收復，前線的戰士紛紛潰逃，而「陪都」摩蘇爾目前也即將被重整歸來的伊拉克政府軍給奪回<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多來，ISIS的部隊已在拉卡周邊舍下重重防禦，除了用地雷帶包圍城市外環外，市區內也佈滿壕溝、地道與城鎮戰陷阱。根據聯軍估計，拉卡周邊還有3-4,000名ISIS戰士，並可能困有16萬以上的平民百姓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於去到最終決戰"},{"pid":"66d90c112019f83bf80875fd126929e63d4833b5","tid":277239,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276422af925228bc9fe13bc05b55a34c039fe2dc","tid":277239,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"豬元帥，飛虎隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87034724e11df3085df32d9fb5d011fb3b5bfb06","tid":277239,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b88ef5a5a580374a91c686de8968c3d2af6bab","tid":277239,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"d俘虜死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8716e842a4b9a7f65b3096393a5441023a655f1","tid":277239,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"就算比你收復哂所有城市<br />\nISIS 最終都未必會滅亡<br />\n<br />\n佢地可以退入山區, 繼續打游擊戰/發動恐襲, 好似塔利班咁<br />\n又可以轉戰去第二個國家, 例如阿富汗, 菲律賓 都有ISIS分支<br />\n<br />\n不過, 其實咁都係好事<br />\n因為ISIS 既勢力和人數都會大量減小, 唔會再好似兩年前咁惡"},{"pid":"9e448b9f18566dcf737f07d78f55f72ff3d17ccb","tid":277239,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"庫德族戰士 20%係女性 我諗起神奇女俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}